OL,3,CCompany linked to Grenfell employed to
OL,4,Cinsulate Tube station near the tower
OL,6,FSadiq Khan said he was angry that an
OL,7,Finsulation company criticised in the
OL,8,FGrenfell Inquiry carried out work at a
OL,9,FTube station closest to the tower.
OL,11,FITV News London found Kingspan
OL,12,Fproducts at Latimer Road station in
OL,13,FWest London and evidence the company
OL,14,Fhas been a client of Transport for
OL,15,FLondon since 2021 with payments worth
OL,16,Fthousands of pounds.
