OL,6,FLondon's mayor said no one responsible
OL,7,Ffor the deadly fire at Grenfell should
OL,8,Fbe getting public contracts and he was
OL,9,Fupset at the impact on people living
OL,10,Fnearby.
OL,12,F"I've asked TFL to look into how this
OL,13,Fhappened," Mr Khan told ITV News
OL,14,FLondon.
OL,16,F"It's not just shameful, it's
OL,17,Fheartbreaking for those residents of
OL,18,Fthat community who've got to see this
OL,19,Fon a regular basis.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
