OL,3,CCompany linked to Grenfell employed to
OL,4,Cinsulate Tube station near the tower
OL,6,F"TfL have made sure that they're
OL,7,Ftaking steps to address this issue.
OL,9,F"I'm angry, not just that Kingspan are
OL,10,Fbenefiting from taxpayers money, I'm
OL,11,Fangry and upset that residents have
OL,12,Fhad their grief and heartbreak
OL,13,Fcompounded," Mr Khan explained.
OL,15,FSince ITV News London began its
OL,16,Finvestigation, Kingsman branding
OL,17,Fappears to have been taken down from
OL,18,FLatimer Road station.
