OL,6,FTransport for London said work to
OL,7,Fremove the insultation would be
OL,8,Ffinished early next week, adding: "We
OL,9,Fare in the process of surveying our
OL,10,Fnetwork and removing Kingspan
OL,11,Finsultation products as necessary.
OL,13,F"The payments relate to agreed annual
OL,14,Fservicing of the ventilation system at
OL,15,Four Acton Works depot and were made
OL,16,Fbefore the publication of the inquiry
OL,17,Freport in September 2024."
