OL,6,FGrenfell Inquiry chairman Sir Martin
OL,7,FMoore-Bick concluded that the
OL,8,Fdevastating fire, which claimed 72
OL,9,Flives, was the result of "decades of
OL,10,Ffailure" by government and the
OL,11,Fconstruction industry to act on the
OL,12,Fdangers of flammable materials on high-
OL,13,Frise buildings.
OL,15,FHe said there had been "systematic
OL,16,Fdishonesty" by firms who made and sold
OL,17,Fthe cladding and insulation, and
OL,18,Fcalled out "deliberate and sustained"
OL,19,Fmanipulation of fire-safety testing,
OL,20,Fmisrepresentation of test data and
OL,21,Fmisleading of the market.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/7
