OL,6,FSadiq Khan said he understood how the
OL,7,Fmaterial at Latimer Road would cause
OL,8,F"real distress", adding: "We've now
OL,9,Fgot the clarity from this government
OL,10,Fwho have made it quite clear when the
OL,11,F(Grenfell Inquiry) report was
OL,12,Fpublished nobody named in the public
OL,13,Finquiry should be receiving any
OL,14,Ftaxpayers money."
OL,16,FKingspan has declined to comment.
